snippet.textDisplay: Know what this game had (that made it such a better game btw) which others didn't? When you won the game, there was still tons more to do. I wish every one of those too-easy games, and even the games that are really good, had a reason for you to keep playing, even after you won. Like Chrono Trigger, for example. And, even once you found everything, there needs to be a secret area that you can get addicted to, like in Kirby Superstar Ultra, the Helper to Hero arena. (Still playing it today :3)
